'''包店'''（Breadtop）是[[澳大利亞|澳大利亞]]的[[麵包店|麵包店]]。出售各種[[甜品|甜品]]、[[蛋糕|蛋糕]]、[[麵包|麵包]]、[[月餅|月餅]]和[[糕點|糕點]]。截至2014年8月，有近69家特許經營門店，遍布大城市[[墨爾本|墨爾本]]、[[悉尼|悉尼]]、[[布里斯班|布里斯班]]、[[阿德莱德|阿德莱德]]和[[堪培拉|堪培拉]]。

==歷史==
包店成立於2002年，其創始人為 Simon Ip 與 Kenneth<ref>{{cite news|last=Cai|first=Peter|title=From $100 in his pocket to a sprawling bun empire|url=http://www.theage.com.au/small-business/entrepreneur/from-100-in-his-pocket-to-a-sprawling-bun-empire-20120529-1zgm1.html|accessdate=31 May 2012|newspaper=The Age|date=2012-05-31|archive-date=2016-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160213053324/http://www.theage.com.au/small-business/entrepreneur/from-100-in-his-pocket-to-a-sprawling-bun-empire-20120529-1zgm1.html|url-status=live}}</ref>，第一家分店設於[[博士山|博士山]]。

截至到2022年5月，包店有近70家門店。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.breadtop.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/store_list.pdf |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-08-21 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140821164936/https://www.breadtop.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/store_list.pdf |archivedate=2014-08-21 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.breadtop.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/20220516_store_list_landscape_without-trading-hour_Edit-by-Kerensa.pdf |title=Breadtop FULL STORE LIST |accessdate=2022-06-08 }}</ref>

